        Constructor.
        Parameters:
        subject - is a subject name,
        teacher - contains information about all teachers, which teach the subject,
        day - is a day when the lecture is taught, may be the empty string,
        time - is a time, when the lecture begins, may be the empty string,
        room - contains information about where the lecture is taught, may be the empty string,
        language - is an indicator of the language the lecture is taught in,
        type - indicates whether this time slot is for the lecture or a practice,
        length - is the length of the lecture in minutes.
